            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            网上攻击公务员，主要集中在这4个方面！          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      北麓                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                湖边看世界              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">湖边看世界</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">fo_gushi</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">湖边看世界，世界在湖边。聊聊体制内那些事，关注官场新生态。 关心官场就是关心自己。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.5546875" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/U5fBOaXlIQl7PWskfibtEOJMTicSaD1pqibFTY6FsWRPzH17s754lxtDMy5etZkTfL0icYspAb41E72X6IichSXKSQg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="height: auto !important;"></span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">网上攻击公务员的现象已经不是什么新鲜事了，但是这种现象背后反映出的是一些人对公务员的认识和态度存在着严重的偏见和误解。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">网上攻击公务员主要集中在以下几个方面：</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">1、攻击公务员不创造社会财富，但工资还那么高，要求公务员只能拿社会平均水平的工资。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这种观点忽略了公务员的工作性质和价值。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员是为国家和社会提供公共服务和管理的专业人员。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">他们的工作虽然不直接创造物质财富，但是对于维护国家安全、社会稳定、法治秩序、民生福祉等方面有着重要的作用。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">没有公务员的辛勤工作，国家和社会就无法正常运转。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员的工资应该根据他们的职责、能力和绩效来确定，而不是简单地按照社会平均水平来划分。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果公务员的工资过低，就会影响他们的工作积极性和效率，也会降低他们的社会地位和尊严，更容易诱发腐败现象。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">2、攻击公务员数量太多，用汉朝2000人养一个公务员的说法来衡量现在公务员实在太多，要求减少公务员数量。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这种观点忽略了时代的变化和国情的差异。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">汉朝时期的社会结构、政治制度、经济发展、科技水平等都与现代社会有着天壤之别，不能用来作为衡量现代公务员数量的标准。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">现代社会的复杂性、多元性、动态性等都要求有足够数量和素质的公务员来应对各种挑战和需求。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我国是一个人口众多、地域广阔、民族多样、发展不平衡的国家，需要有一个强大而有效的政府来统筹协调各方面的事务。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我国目前有700多万名公务员，占总人口的0.5%，低于世界平均水平。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我国政府也一直在推进简政放权、优化服务、提高效能等改革措施，适当调整和优化公务员队伍结构和规模。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">3、攻击公务员退休金高，要求公务员跟工人和农民看齐。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这种观点忽略了公务员退休金制度的特点和合理性。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我国实行了多层次的养老保障体系，包括基本养老保险、企业年金、职业年金、个人储蓄养老保险等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">其中，职业年金是针对特定行业或领域设立的一种补充性养老保险制度，目的是为了鼓励和吸引优秀人才从事相关领域的工作，并给予他们适当的福利待遇。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我国目前已经建立了教师职业年金、公务员职业年金、企业高管职业年金等多种职业年金制度。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员退休金是由基本养老保险和公务员职业年金两部分组成的，其中公务员职业年金是由公务员个人和政府共同缴纳的，不是从社会保险基金中划拨的。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员退休金的制度设计是符合国情和国际惯例的，也是对公务员长期服务国家和社会的一种奖励和保障。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">4、攻击公务员不做事，整天一张报纸一杯茶，遇到一点难办的事，所有的情绪都可以发泄到公务员身上。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这种观点忽略了公务员的工作实际和困难。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员的工作并不像有些人想象的那么轻松和舒适，而是充满了压力和挑战。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员要面对各种复杂的政策法规、繁琐的程序流程、多样的利益诉求、紧迫的工作任务等，还要承受来自上级、下级、同事、群众等各方面的监督和评价。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">公务员要时刻保持高度的责任感和敬业精神，不断学习和提高自己的专业能力和素养，为国家和社会做出贡献。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">当然，也不能否认，有些公务员确实存在着懒惰、消极、推诿、拖延等不良现象，这些都应该受到批评和惩处。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">但是，不能因为个别现象而否定整体情况，不能因为偏见而无视事实。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">综上所述，网上片面攻击公务员的现象是一种不理性和不正义的行为，它既损害了公务员的合法权益和尊严，也影响了政府部门与社会民众之间的沟通和信任。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">我们应该客观地看待和评价公务员的工作和作用。</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1019907637" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
